description: List Assets in the Media Services account with optional filtering and ordering

subscription_id.description: The unique identifier for a Microsoft Azure subscription.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group within the Azure subscription.

api_version.description: The Version of the API to be used with the client request.

filter.description: Restricts the set of items returned.

top.description: Specifies a non-negative integer n that limits the number of items returned from a collection. The service returns the number of available items up to but not greater than the specified value n.

orderby.description: Specifies the key by which the result collection should be ordered.
